pageTitle: Prime Minister’s itinerary for Wednesday, September 28, 2022 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Note: All times local

Channel-Port aux Basques, Newfoundland and Labrador

Private meetings

The Prime Minister will speak with the President of Ukraine, Volodymyr Zelenskyy.

The Prime Minister will meet with local community members impacted by Hurricane Fiona. Premier of Newfoundland and Labrador Andrew Furey, Minister of Rural Economic Development Gudie Hutchings, and Minister of Labour Seamus O’Regan Jr. will also be in attendance.

Note for media:

  • Pooled coverage
